quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,25,"aur aepeghambar, jo log is kitaab par imaan le ayen aur ( is ke mutabiq ) apne amal durust kar lain, inhen khush khaberi day do ke unn ke liye aisay baagh hain, jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi un baghoon ke phal soorat mein duniya ke phalon se mlitay jaltay hunge jab koi phal inhen khanay ko diya jaye ga, to woh kahin ge ke aisay hi phal is se pehlay duniya mein hum ko diye jatay thay un ke liye wahan pakeeza biwiyan hongi, aur woh wahan hamesha rahen ge"
2,26,"haan, Allah is se hargiz nahi sharmaata ke machar ya is se bhi haqeer tar kisi cheez kitamselain day jo log haq baat ko qubool karne walay hain, woh unhi tamseloonko dekh kar jaan letay hain ke yeh haq hai jo un ke Rab hi ki taraf se aaya hai, aur jo maan-ne walay nahi hain, woh inhen sun kar kehnay lagtay hain ke aisi tamseloonse Allah ko kya sarokaar? is terhan Allah aik hi baat se bahuton ko gumraahi mein mubtala kar deta hai aur bahuton ko raah raast dikha deta hai aur gumraahi mein woh unhi ko mubtala karta hai, jo fasik hain"
2,27,"Allah ke ehad ko mazboot bandh lainay ke baad toar dete hain Allah ne jisay jornay ka hukum diya hai ussay kaat tay hain, aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa karte hain haqeeqat mein yahi log nuqsaan uthany walay hain"
2,28,"tum Allah ke sath kufar ka rawayya kaisay ikhtiyar karte ho halaank tum bayjaan thay, is ne tum ko zindagi ataa ki, phir wohi tumhari jaan salb kere ga, phir wohi tumhe dobarah zindagi ataa kere ga, phir isi ki taraf tumhe palat kar jana hai"
2,29,"wohi to hai, jis ne tumahray liye zameen ki saari cheeze peedakee, phir oopar ki taraf tavajja farmai aur saat aasman ustuwar kiye aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhnay wala hai"
